content.text: 1.There is no cash payment in lieu of shares in the TMT Portfolio
Composition File today. Estimated Cash Component Per Basket is NT$23,850
2.The Manager will give notice of the Cash Payment Amount after 4 pm on
Creation Day.
3.The announcement of the above information was made in accordance with
Article 36 of the 「Yuanta/P-shares Taiwan Mid-Cap 100 ETF Trust Agreement
」 The contents of the information were supplied by Yuanta Investment
Trust Co. Ltd. on 2024/03/29 The contents of this Portfolio
Composition File are based on the Chinese version of the announcement
made by Yuanta Investment Trust Co. Ltd. For other related information
and electronic information, please refer to the web site.
(http://www.yuantaetfs.com)
1.本日實物申購清單中無規定採用現金替代之成份標的。每實物申購單位估計現金差額
（即預估基準現金差額）為$23,850元
2.每實物申購單位之實際現金差額於申請日下午四點後，以基金經理公司通知給付之金
額為準。
3.以上資料係依據「元大台灣中型100證券投資信託基金證券投資信託契約」第三十六條
之規定公告，資料內容由元大投信2024/03/29提供。
實物申購買回清單內容以公告之中文版本為準，其餘相關資訊及電子資料請參考網址
(http://www.yuantaetfs.com)。
